overview: Global Discovery Vacations is known for offering excellent vacation packages and efficient customer support services. The members of this flexible membership program pay the annual activity fee only if they intend to travel or use any benefits of their membership. Global Discovery Vacations allows its members to enjoy condominium vacation accommodations plus cruise, tour packages, and a buying service offering the latest brand name products at reasonable prices.
